===Noun===
{{en-noun|~}}

# {{lb|en|uncountable}} The attribute or characteristic of acting in [[secrecy]], or in such a way that the actions are unnoticed or difficult to detect by others.
# {{lb|en|archaic|countable}} An act of secrecy, especially one involving [[thievery]].
